metadata.name: Ex Cyclopedia: Departure #1/10
metadata.description:
Her father’s boat were moored at the Moody Vicar’s. 
The next morning she set out. 
The skies were cold and unclear.

This XCLPD special 1/10 edition was created to mark the upcoming 10th episode of Ex Cyclopedia.

╳╳╳ 
Hand drawn digital artwork. The colours and textures were derived from processed paper ephemera.  Original size: 6310×6310 px, jpeg
